<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>新闻—首页</title>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, maximum-scale=1">
  <meta name="x5-orientation" content="portrait">
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="static/plugins/layui-v2.5.6/layui/css/layui.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="static/plugins/layuiSimpleNews/index.css">
  <style>
    @media screen and (min-width: 320px)and (max-width: 750px){
      /* 横屏 */
      @media (orientation: landscape) {
        #newsIndex,
        img.carousesImg,
        .news-index .contentTop #newsIndex [carousel-item]{
          height: 300px !important;
        }
      }
      /* 竖屏 */
      @media (orientation: portrait) {
        #newsIndex,
        img.carousesImg,
        .news-index .contentTop #newsIndex [carousel-item]{
          height: 200px !important;
        }
      }

      .news-index .contentTop #newsIndex #txt{
        height: 57px;
      }
      .news-index .contentTop #newsIndex .layui-carousel-ind{
        top: -27px;
      }
      span#carouselName{
        overflow: hidden;
        text-overflow: ellipsis;
        white-space: nowrap;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
<!-- 头部导航 -->
<%- include('./index_header.ejs') %>
<div class="layui-container news-index">
	<div class="layui-row layui-col-space20 contentTop">
    <div class="layui-col-sm8">
      <!-- 首页轮播图 -->
      <%- include('./index_carousel.ejs') %>
    </div>
    <div class="layui-col-xs6 layui-col-sm4">
     	<div class="banner-img">
	     	<img src="static/plugins/layuiSimpleNews/demoImg/home_img2.jpg">
	     	<div><p><span>娱乐</span>明星给自己颜值打分，王源7分，杨颖满分，千玺的回答圈粉无数</p></div>
     	</div>
    </div>
    <div class="layui-col-xs6 layui-col-sm4">
     	<div class="banner-img">
	     	<img src="static/plugins/layuiSimpleNews/demoImg/home_img3.jpg">
	     	<div><p><span>科技</span>华为手机这 3 个功能实用又有趣，不知道就可惜了！</p></div>
     	</div>
    </div>
	 </div>
	<div class="layui-row layui-col-space20 contentBot">
    <div class="layui-col-md8 index-list">
    	<h2>推荐新闻</h2>
    	<ul class="newsList">
			<% for( var i=0;i<articles.length;i++){ %>
				<% if( articles[i].category_url == 'tuijian' ) { %>
					<li>
						<a class="img" href="javascript:;"><img src="<%= articles[i].cover %>"></a><div class="txt">
							<a href="/articleDetail<%= articles[i].id %>"><%= articles[i].title %></a>
							<div class="label">
								<span><%= articles[i].label %></span><%= articles[i].source %> 
								<b><%= articles[i].update_time %></b> 
								<i class="layui-icon layui-icon-news-review1"></i><%= articles[i].read_count %>
							</div>
							<p class="cont"><%= articles[i].summary %></p>
						</div>
					</li>
				<% } %>
			<% } %>
    	</ul>
    	<!-- <div class="btn"><a href="javascript:;" class="layui-btn layui-btn-primary">点击加载更多</a></div>		 -->
    </div>
    <div class="layui-col-md4 index-side">
    	<div class="newsSide">
	     	<h2>24小时热文</h2>
	     	<ul>
	     		<li><a href="javascript:;"><span><img src="static/plugins/layuiSimpleNews/demoImg/home_img10.jpg"></span><p class="txt">今日魔都烟雾缭绕，美似仙境！</p></a></li>
	     		<li><a href="javascript:;"><span><img src="static/plugins/layuiSimpleNews/demoImg/home_img11.jpg"></span><p class="txt">美计划调高对华商品征税税率 外交部：施压与讹诈不会起作用</p></a></li>
	     		<li><a href="javascript:;"><span><img src="static/plugins/layuiSimpleNews/demoImg/home_img12.jpg"></span><p class="txt">烟草纳税万亿！一包20元的烟利润 是多少钱？烟民：为了纳税而抽烟</p></a></li>
	     		<li><a href="javascript:;"><span><img src="static/plugins/layuiSimpleNews/demoImg/home_img13.jpg"></span><p class="txt">移动端游戏占领大部分市场</p></a></li>
	     		<li><a href="javascript:;"><span><img src="static/plugins/layuiSimpleNews/demoImg/home_img14.jpg"></span><p class="txt">八一建军节天安门升旗仪式</p></a></li>
	     		<li><a href="javascript:;"><span><img src="static/plugins/layuiSimpleNews/demoImg/home_img10.jpg"></span><p class="txt">今日魔都烟雾缭绕，美似仙境！</p></a></li>
	     		<li><a href="javascript:;"><span><img src="static/plugins/layuiSimpleNews/demoImg/home_img11.jpg"></span><p class="txt">美计划调高对华商品征税税率 外交 部：施压与讹诈不会起作用</p></a></li>
	     		<li><a href="javascript:;"><span><img src="static/plugins/layuiSimpleNews/demoImg/home_img12.jpg"></span><p class="txt">烟草纳税万亿！一包20元的烟利润 是多少钱？烟民：为了纳税而抽烟</p></a></li>
	     		<li><a href="javascript:;"><span><img src="static/plugins/layuiSimpleNews/demoImg/home_img13.jpg"></span><p class="txt">移动端游戏占领大部分市场</p></a></li>
	     		<li><a href="javascript:;"><span><img src="static/plugins/layuiSimpleNews/demoImg/home_img14.jpg"></span><p class="txt">八一建军节天安门升旗仪式</p></a></li>
	     	</ul>
	    </div>
    </div>
	</div>
  <div id="silde"><a id="refresh"><i class="layui-icon layui-icon-refresh"></i></a><a id="scroll"><i class="layui-icon layui-icon-up"></i></a></div>
</div>

<div class="news-footer">
  <div class="layui-container">
    <span class="layui-breadcrumb" lay-separator=" ">
      <a>关于我们</a>
      <a>合作伙伴</a>
      <a>广告服务</a>
      <a>常见问题</a>
    </span>
    <p class="copyright">Copyright &copy; <%= webSiteconfig.copyright %></p>
    <a id="wechat" href=""><i class="layui-icon layui-icon-news-wechat"></i></a>
    <a id="weibo" href=""><i class="layui-icon layui-icon-news-weibo"></i></a>
    <img id="code" src="static/plugins/layuiSimpleNews/demoImg/code.png">
  </div>
</div>

<script src="static/plugins/layui-v2.5.6/layui/layui.js"></script>
